    "body": "I think I know what's happening. I didn't create the `jwtsecret` before running. Besu does not create the token automatically. If the token does not exist it reverts to creating `jwt.hex` and does not create it automatically. This is different than the other execution clients.\r\n\r\nYa'll can close this if this is the expected behavior.",
